These are Puzzles for 2x2 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-8-1::.
2 different pets are kept: lizard, hamster
The people use 2 different means of transport: airplane, scooter
1. the person driving the airplane is on the right of the person driving the scooter##1
2. the owner of the lizard is not to the right of the person driving the scooter##8

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |    2     |
| Pet        | lizard   | hamster   |
| Transport   | scooter | airplane |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-8-2::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: juice, soy-milk
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: january, december
1. the person who's birthday is in january is not to the left of the person drinking soy-milk##8
2. the person who's birthday is in january is somewhere to the right of the person drinking soy-milk##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |    2    |
| Beverage   | soy-milk | juice   |
| Birthday      | december | january |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-8-3::.
There 2 different types of food: cabbage, peach
There are 2 different favourite beverages: coffee, cola
1. the person eating cabbage is not to the left of the person drinking cola##8
2. the person eating peach is on the left of the person drinking cola##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |    2    |
| Food          | peach | cabbage |
| Beverage   | coffee   | cola     |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-8-4::.
